    "Professional bodies must assume additional responsibilities regarding the development and use of AI based tools.",
    "Supervision is central to clinical training in SLP, encompassing the mentorship of students, assistants, and early-career professionals.",
    "AI tools can enhance this process by analyzing session recordings, generating performance analytics, and tracking clinical hours for secure reporting to professional bodies like ASHA.",
    "AI agents, won't get tired, will work round the clock, and may offer consistent, scalable support for routine supervision tasks (Brockenbrough, 2022).",
    "Such tools may standardize oversight, highlight growth areas, and improve the reliability of performance feedback."
